            <h3>Installation Carried Out</h3>
            <p>Our own Gas Safe engineers carry out the full installation. We protect floors, work neatly and clean up fully each day. Most standard installations take 3 to 5 days.</p>
            <span class="step-note">3 to 5 days typical</span>
          </div>
